snippet.title: Stalker film. Zone 66. Episode 1. Amber Dawn. eng subs
snippet.description: After the falling of unidentified object named in the news as meteorite, in the area of the fallen object the strange things, unexplainable in terms of modern science, had been coming. An expanding area of abnormal phenomena named as Zone 66 had built up. Defense officials cordon the perimeter of the Zone in attempt to suppress the expansion. At the same time, the locals, who heard about the items of incredible value, went to the Zone seeking easy money. Such people were named stalkers. The series is telling about the adventures of stalker named Hiker, who went to the Zone after sanguinary killing of his family. The murderer organized his own gang named "Lawyers".
